{"id":232895505,"title":"家人覺得騎FNX上課太高調= =","content":"跟爸媽討論要買車代步，剛剛拿手機秀我想買的FNX給他們看 \nhttp://i.imgur.com/Tc5jWEA.png\n  \n👨：妳要騎這台?沒有其他顏色嗎?\n👧：對啊不覺得外觀很有設計感嗎~\n👩：紅色是漂亮啦，但妳騎一台這麼新的車去不怕被偷?\n👨：對啦對啦，不要買這麼顯眼的車，容易引人側目太高調了\n\n然後媽媽還補一句說，學生代步而已不用買這麼漂亮的車，可以騎就好…\n\n先說買車錢我自己貸36期0利率，所以都我自己出\n只是想跟爸媽討論一下我準備要買FNX，紅色會隨著光影變化明明超有設計感，很適合女生騎吧!?為什麼學生就不應該騎漂亮的車勒…估計等等吃晚餐我爸媽又要繼續念我了，大家買車怎麼過家人這關的?","excerpt":"跟爸媽討論要買車代步，剛剛拿手機秀我想買的FNX給他們看，：妳要騎這台？沒有其他顏色嗎？：對啊不覺得外觀很有設計感嗎~，：紅色是漂亮啦，但妳騎一台這麼新的車去不怕被偷？：對啦對啦，不要買這麼顯眼的車，","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d208d1e2-6f14-429b-97b7-75a2dd4f761c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-15T10:34:33.153Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T10:34:33.153Z","commentCount":139,"likeCount":607,"tags":[],"topics":["機車","FNX"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"汽機車","forumAlias":"vehicle","school":"世新大學","department":"數位媒體設計學系","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":596},{"id":"e8e6bc5d-41b0-4129-b134-97507523d7ff","count":10},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/Tc5jWEA.png"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"5edeb16f-8828-477b-b8cf-1cb4332eb2f0","url":"https://i.imgur.com/Tc5jWEAl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/Tc5jWEAl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Tc5jWEAl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-15T10:34:33.153Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T10:34:33.153Z"},{"id":"5edeb16f-8828-477b-b8cf-1cb4332eb2f0","url":"http://i.imgur.com/Tc5jWEA.png","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/Tc5jWEA","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/Tc5jWEAl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-15T10:34:33.153Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-15T10:34: